Yes, she does.
She's a genius.

45
00:01:30,391 --> 00:01:31,975
All right if I complete
my rounds now?

46
00:01:32,059 --> 00:01:34,544
Or is she such a genius that
she can look after herself?

47
00:01:34,628 --> 00:01:36,780
No. Go ahead.
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

48
00:01:36,864 --> 00:01:38,448
Wilson, Chief,

49
