Still do.

62
00:02:10,397 --> 00:02:11,982
Okay.

63
00:02:12,066 --> 00:02:13,150
Baby or laundry?

64
00:02:13,234 --> 00:02:14,217
Neither.

65
00:02:14,301 --> 00:02:15,552
I... I just want
everything to stop.

66
00:02:15,636 --> 00:02:17,721
The whole planet,
it can just stop turning,

67
00:02:17,805 --> 00:02:19,022
and we can all
just melt.

68
00:02:19,106 --> 00:02:20,190
Is it for us?

69
00:02:20,274 --> 00:02:21,458
Is it for us?

70
00:02:21,542 --> 00:02:22,759
Is it for us?

71
