Karissa, you can't get up. We're
waiting on neuro to see you.

223
00:08:00,247 --> 00:08:01,197
Okay? Just squeeze.
I'm fine, I'm fine.

224
00:08:01,281 --> 00:08:02,198
But my boyfriend...
Husband...

225
00:08:02,282 --> 00:08:03,199
Uh, he...
He hates needles.

226
00:08:03,283 --> 00:08:04,300
He really hates needles.

227
00:08:04,384 --> 00:08:05,635
He's being worked on
by excellent doctors.

228
00:08:05,719 --> 00:08:06,703
Can you follow my finger?

229
00:08:06,787 --> 00:08:07,871
But can't you put us
in the same room?

230
00:08:07,955 --> 00:08:09,205
I really need
to talk to him.

231
00:08:09,289 --> 00:08:10,240
When we were
in the accident,

232
00:08:10,324 --> 00:08:11,941
I kinda said a thing,
and I feel terrible.

233
00:08:12,025 --> 00:08:14,110
Well, you're in luck. They pay
me to help people who feel terrible.

234
00:08:14,194 --> 00:08:15,612
Any loss of consciousness?
Dizziness?

235
00:08:15,696 --> 00:08:16,613
I don't think so.

236
00:08:16,697 --> 00:08:18,281
So, what?
You cheated on him?

237
00:08:18,365 --> 00:08:20,283
You stole all his money?
You ran over grandma?

238
00:08:20,367 --> 00:08:22,118
Okay, CT's calling for her.
Do you want to come?

239
00:08:22,202 --> 00:08:23,586
Please and thank you.
Squeeze my hands, please.

240
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,889
I told the paramedics
to save me first.

241
00:08:25,973 --> 00:08:27,390
Over him, my husband.

242
00:08:27,474 --> 00:08:30,226
Yikes. Well, maybe you can
blame that on a brain bleed.

243
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:32,162
Can you please tell him
I'm okay?

244
00:08:32,246 --> 00:08:34,330
Yeah.
Let's go.

245
00:08:34,414 --> 00:08:35,899
You know
what else she said?

246
00:08:35,983 --> 00:08:39,035
That except for her, no one
would miss me if I died.

247
00:08:39,119 --> 00:08:41,871
She thinks I'm a loner
